### 13. MODEL STORAGE LAYOUT

Models are stored in `$OLLAMA_MODELS` (default: `~/.ollama/models/`) with this structure:

```
~/.ollama/models/
├── manifests/
│   └── registry.ollama.ai/
│       └── library/
│           ├── llama2/
│           │   ├── latest       (manifest file - JSON)
│           │   └── 13b          (manifest file - JSON)
│           └── mistral/
│               └── latest
├── blobs/
│   ├── sha256-abcd1234...
│   ├── sha256-efgh5678...
│   └── ... (referenced by multiple manifests)
```

**Key insight:** Manifests are small JSON files, while blobs (weights) are shared. Delete removes manifest + unreferenced blobs. Copy only copies the manifest file.

